This project is based on astro-blog-zozo by Ladit:
https://github.com/ladit/astro-blog-zozo

astro-blog-zozo was inspired by hugo-theme-zozo by varkai:
https://github.com/varkai/hugo-theme-zozo

Revamped Astro Zozo is a derivative theme branch that extends the upstream project with revised layouts, a gallery system, a friends page, updated navigation interactions, and a sample-first content structure.

Original license and copyright notices are retained in LICENSE.

Code in this repository remains subject to the upstream MIT license unless otherwise noted.

Bundled sample copy and placeholder SVG assets in this branch are included for demonstration so the theme can be previewed immediately. Replace them with your own branding and materials before publishing a production site.
